item.title: About
item.description: About me My name is Nhat Minh Nguyen, but these days I usually go with “Nathan”. I am from Saigon, Vietnam. I currently live in Brisbane after moving here at the beginning of 2020. I am expecting to graduate from the University of Queensland this December, with a Bachelor’s (Honours) degree in Software Engineering. Experience My first ever job was a part-time job as a teaching assistant at a programming school named Big-O Coding in Saigon.
